metadata.description:
What's up some guys!!! Against all odds, we managed to eke out another lil banger –– time to immortalize it on-chain. 

"Can We Talk?" is special for us because it's the most collaborative song we've made to date. We got to work with our friends (Tyler Hentges) and producers that are also friends (Clayjay + Michael Garmany) to come up with something a bit different. 

We have loved, argued over, revised, and enjoyed this song as a demo for a while now –– now it's your turn! 

Hope you like it <3

lyrics.text:
Can we talk?
Somewhere alone
A shot in the dark
A kiss through the phone
How could you believe
You were special to me
It’s really bustin’ me up
It just gets hard to breathe

And I'm so lifted by your touch
This fucking around
Is fucking me up
Can we talk?
And I said ooo, my love
There’s just something about ya
I just can’t keep getting on
Ooo damn without your support
Oh, I know you wanna bombs away
When I’m never knowin’ what to say
And I'm so lifted by your touch

I need something to hold

My shelter
